.PP
Returns the FIPS operating status of crypto and the underlying libcrypto library. If crypto was built with FIPS support this can be either \fIenabled\fR (when running in FIPS mode) or \fInot_enabled\fR. For other builds this value is always \fInot_supported\fR.

