.PP
Argument \fIType\fR is the type of MAC and \fIData\fR is the full message.

.PP
\fISubType\fR depends on the MAC \fIType\fR:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
For \fIhmac\fR it is a hash algorithm, see Algorithm Details in the User's Guide.

