.PP
Algorithm \fIdss\fR can only be used together with digest type \fIsha\fR.

.PP
Uses the 3-tuple style for error handling.

.PP
See also \fIpublic_key:sign/3\fR.


.RE
.B
\fBstart() -> ok | {error, Reason :: term()}.\fR

.RS
.LP
Deprecated: crypto:start/0 is deprecated; use application:start(crypto) instead
.RE

.br
.RS
.PP
Use \fIapplication:start(crypto)\fR instead.

.PP
\fBWARNING: \fRThis function does not work if FIPS mode is to be enabled. FIPS mode will be disabled even if configuration parameter \fIfips_mode\fR is set to \fItrue\fR. Use \fIapplication:start(crypto)\fR instead.



.RE
